            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* Request $9 billion for NASA's Science Mission Directorate to restore program stability and maintain US leadership in space.\n* Supports essential missions across planetary science, astrophysics, and Earth observation guided by National Academies' Decadal Surveys.\n* Provides necessary funding to counter rapid expansion of international space programs and ensure the U.S. sets 21st-century exploration norms.",
