            "draft_value": "* NASA Science funding directly supports the local economy through contracts with NV-03 firms like Rimini Street, Inc. in Las Vegas for IT infrastructure.\n* District-based businesses including Hsg, LLC ($1.25M in recent awards) and Aldec Inc provide specialized technical services essential to NASA missions.\n* Sustained investment preserves a high-tech workforce in Nevada and strengthens the STEM pipeline for the state's growing aerospace and technology sectors.",
